{"id": "work_90055143-ae48-5351-809b-3245d388524f", "title": "Black-Box Superconducting Circuit Quantization", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1042785878"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:36:41.000899", "abstract": "We present a semiclassical method for determining the effective low-energy quantum Hamiltonian of weakly anharmonic superconducting circuits containing mesoscopic Josephson junctions coupled to electromagnetic environments made of an arbitrary combination of distributed and lumped elements. A convenient basis, capturing the multimode physics, is given by the quantized eigenmodes of the linearized circuit and is fully determined by a classical linear response function. The method is used to calculate numerically the low-energy spectrum of a 3D transmon system, and quantitative agreement with measurements is found.", "publication_date": "2012-06-12", "doi": "10.1103/physrevlett.108.240502", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1042785878?and_facet_researcher=ur.015527265674.84", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_08193ae5-fe0e-5d14-a265-b3b7b1442db3", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_a8e8a052-5104-520d-b353-69d002d6b476", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_8d6a024e-9c10-578a-bb58-85bde55a929c", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_6e7db33e-e505-5c7a-8c36-a20775d68ae6", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_efcff76a-9f19-5e6f-bec0-51e13fce22c6", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_d2b8b900-5488-5f87-ab9d-06fb3b0ff50b", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_f3887ae3-1997-5c7c-bacd-477f516abf7d", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_b7f874c0-f80b-59b0-ae92-d836f62f2b84", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}, {"author_id": "author_05d4b046-8319-56cd-a216-425dff836a4f", "org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df"}], "orgs": [{"org_id": "org_cf6683eb-25ad-50fe-a19d-855f6e3e86df", "role": "affiliation"}], "topics": [{"topic_id": "topic_40c92d30-1e13-51c2-a6bc-692493c876ff", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_7ced97ac-1108-5195-b3a2-d664e9eb9af5", "score": 1.0}], "created_at": "2026-03-09T19:36:41.000899"}